# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and the working tree (#81).
# The repo had drifted into mixed CRLF/LF (some files internally mixed),
# which turned small edits into thousand-line diffs whenever an editor
# normalized. One renormalization commit accompanies this file.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets -- never touch
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.PNG binary
*.JPG binary
